reviewText: This is a historical study of the Packard automobile company and its downfall. This is a capture of the original History Channel broadcast and an expanded edition is now available via DVD.

Finally a Genealogy Documentary! Our genealogy group donated this DVD our local public library in memory of a friend and felloow genealogy buff. It is a nice addition to any library or personal collection. Nicely done.
you`ll have a total different look the next time when going to the aquarium, good job well done. highly recommended.
This DVD guides you through steps taken to look at the family history of different individuals.  It also gives you information on how to go about getting information about your own family history.
